.TH "SFARKXTC" 1 "2026-03-01" "20181208" "SlackBuilds.org"
.SH NAME
sfarkxtc \- extract sfArk v2 files
.\" RST source for sfarkxtc(1) man page. Convert with:
.
.\" rst2man.py sfarkxtc.rst > sfarkxtc.1
.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.sp
sfarkxtc \fBinput\-file\fP \fI<output\-file>\fP
.SH DESCRIPTION
.sp
sfarkxtc is a console utility to convert soundfonts in the legacy
sfArk v2 file format to sf2. sfArk is a lossless audio compression
format optimized for SoundFont files. Only v2 sfArk archives are
supported.
.sp
\fBinput\-file\fP must be a v2 sfArk file. Typically these have filenames
ending in \fB\&.sfArk\fP\&.
.sp
The output will be the result as a SoundFont (sf2) file. If no
\fIoutput\-file\fP is given, the original filename stored in the .sfArk
file is used.
